author: xsteve
msg: Out of the box support for non english svn clients + a minor fix
* trunk/contrib/client-side/psvn/psvn.el:
(svn-status-svn-environment-var-list): Set it to LANG=C
to make psvn.el work out of the box with non english svn clients
(svn-log-revision-at-point): Bugfix to make it do the correct thing
independent from the cursor position on the current line

author: dlr
msg: A follow-up to r21628, fixing the SWIG/Python bindings by working
around the inability of the header file parser used for SWIG code
generation to handle anonymous structs.
This could be fixed in a proper fashion by changing the regular
expressions used to parse the header files in header_wrappers.py.
* subversion/include/svn_wc.h
(svn_wc_entry_callbacks2_t): Name the struct to keep the SWIG
bindings happy.
